[LinkGun]
; EN: Description="Riordan Dynamic Weapon Systems combines the best of weapon design in the Advanced Plasma Rifle v23, commonly known as the Link Gun.|While the primary firing mode of the Link remains the same as its plasma-firing predecessor, the secondary cutting torch has been replaced with a switchable energy matrix. Upon contacting a teammate, it converts to a harmless carrier stream, offloading energy from the onboard cells to boost the output of any targeted player also using the Link.|It should be noted that while players are boosting a teammate, they are unable to defend themselves from attack."
Description="Riordan Dynamic Weapon Systems kombinerar det bûÊsta av vapendesign i Advanced Plasma Rifle v23, allmûÊnt kûÊnd som Link Gun.|Medan det primûÊra avfyrningslûÊget fûÑr Link fûÑrblir detsamma som dess fûÑregûËngare fûÑr plasmaavfyrning, har den sekundûÊra skûÊrbrûÊnnaren ersatts med en omkopplingsbar energimatris. NûÊr den kontaktar en lagkamrat omvandlas den till en ofarlig bûÊrarstrûÑm, som avlastar energi frûËn cellerna ombord fûÑr att ûÑka uteffekten frûËn alla mûËlspelare som ocksûË anvûÊnder lûÊnken.|Det bûÑr noteras att medan spelare ûÑkar en lagkamrat, kan de inte fûÑrsvara sig. sig frûËn attack."
