; EN: Description="The Trident Tri-barrel Rocket Launcher is extremely popular among competitors who enjoy more bang for their buck.|The rotating rear loading barrel design allows for both single- and multi-warhead launches, letting you place up to three dumb fire rockets on target.|The warheads are designed to deliver maximum concussive force to the target and surrounding area upon detonation."
Description="Trident Tri-barrel Rocket Launcher ûÊr extremt populûÊr bland konkurrenter som tycker om mer valuta fûÑr pengarna.|Den roterande bakre laddningspipans design mûÑjliggûÑr uppskjutning av bûËde en- och multistridsspetsar, vilket lûËter dig placera upp till tre dumma eldraketer pûË mûËlet. Stridsspetsarna ûÊr designade fûÑr att leverera maximal hjûÊrnskakning till mûËlet och det omgivande omrûËdet vid detonation."
