[ShieldGun]
; EN: Description="The Kemphler DD280 Riot Control Device has the ability to resist and reflect incoming projectiles and energy beams. The plasma wave inflicts massive damage, rupturing tissue, pulverizing organs, and flooding the bloodstream with dangerous gas bubbles.||This weapon may be intended for combat at close range, but when wielded properly should be considered as dangerous as any other armament in your arsenal."
Description="Kemphler DD280 Riot Control Device har fûÑrmûËgan att motstûË och reflektera inkommande projektiler och energistrûËlar. PlasmavûËgen orsakar massiv skada, spricker vûÊvnad, pulveriserar organ och svûÊmmar ûÑver blodomloppet med farliga gasbubblor.||Detta vapen kan vara avsett fûÑr strid pûË nûÊra hûËll, men nûÊr det anvûÊnds pûË rûÊtt sûÊtt bûÑr det anses vara lika farligt som alla andra vapen i din arsenal."
